{"tid":424333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟：授權西班牙以武抗獨","createTime":"2017-10-04T14:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T05:03:43.000Z","uid":41351,"like":9,"dislike":150,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"7248571048211db0a3b14eab0e594fa75fdd0836","tid":424333,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"西班牙東北部的加泰隆尼亞危機不斷升高，歐盟執行委員會今天(4日)表示，是針對解決危機進行會談的時候了。不過，執委會仍然捍衛馬德里當局，有權利動用「相稱的」武力以維持法律與秩序。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟執委會副主席(Frans Timmermans)在歐洲議會召開的辯論中說，現在是進行會談的時候了，以在西班牙憲政秩序運作之下，尋找化解僵局之道。<br />\n<br />\n加泰隆尼亞1日在西班牙鎮暴警察的暴力鎮壓之下，仍然通過獨立公投，並計畫在近日內宣布獨立，不但升高了與西班牙政府之間的緊張，也令歐盟各國備感關切。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rti.org.tw/m/news/detail/?recordId=372406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F%3FrecordId%3D372406&d=Xx60%2Bn2YubjkVl70vg4iBgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=7a65f619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rti.org.tw/m/news/detail/?recordId=372406</a><br />\n邪惡歐盟"},{"pid":"c3987040c7fe2ea371cb11857b9a743881e56f7a","tid":424333,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:55:00.000Z","msg":"相稱的武力<br />\n可圈可點"},{"pid":"29b030182993a6edd01b45814e9f3938bc2ac757","tid":424333,"uid":81150,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"可恥"},{"pid":"080540b0ebb62033fe7b94602a3752f78b0421b8","tid":424333,"uid":29784,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>相稱的武力<br />\n可圈可點</blockquote><br />\n中文拎咩"},{"pid":"4f6afa8a8ab7a9b979d8f91a7fc68d11f52f03b0","tid":424333,"uid":41351,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:59:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>相稱的武力<br />\n可圈可點</blockquote><br />\n中文拎咩</blockquote><br />\n即係睇下加泰抵抗有幾強烈<br />\n加泰越強西班牙可更強以作壓制"},{"pid":"1e1944b62e284c99c31ecea9dc75793fb3c39693","tid":424333,"uid":2054,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T15:00:04